Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:24.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't disturb him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:29.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He has passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be a fruit knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become a grave situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:47.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:50.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It penetrated his notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:54.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The perpetrator must possess considerable physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:56.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it would be safe to assume that the perpetrator was male.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:03.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the fact that Yutaka Tamaru-san is nowhere to be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:04.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:07.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably shouldn't tell Little Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:09.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be best if we didn't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn of events requires some deliberation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:17.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation is, for all intents and purposes, a closed circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And at first glance, it would also appear to be homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:21.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it happened in a locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:26.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.99,0:01:30.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...how could the perpetrator commit the crime in this inaccessible room...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and make his getaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:17.62,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,490)\fs24\pos(340,397)}Remote Island Syndrome (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san is in bed after suddenly falling ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we have to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:29.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the door locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open it for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have imagined something like this happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:55.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you talking about how badly you wanted something to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wasn't expecting something to actually happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A murder in a locked room on an island during a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:05.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is the probability of an incident like that occurring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...at our destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe this also happened because Haruhi wished for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She looked like a mischievous boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...after an April Fool's joke gone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't want to consider this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't Yutaka-san the main suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan mentioned something yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them were fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it looked that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the bathroom in the middle of our game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when I was at this same spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:51.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prepare a passport and traveler's checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...he could have been arranging his escape to another country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But why the locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No attempt was made to make it look like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to bother setting it up in a locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stand around and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go take another close look at Keiichi-san's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:20.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was instructed not to allow anyone inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When will the police be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the forecast...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:27.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the weather will have improved by tomorrow afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I suppose they will arrive sometime in that vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the door locked all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I only tried knocking on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:42.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san has documents pertaining to his work in his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:45.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I am prohibited from opening the door when he doesn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Keiichi-san and Yutaka-san not get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason being that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:06:01.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mori and I have only been working here for one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are part-timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:09.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporarily hired butler and maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:13.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our contract was brief, a mere two weeks of this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was just for this villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't previously employed by Keiichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as the brothers are concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:27.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I am only aware that Yutaka-sama is an employee at Keiichi-sama's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something isn't right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this strange feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:40.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:41.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was patrolling the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-san is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:48.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going out to check if the boat's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that the boat is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-sama appeared to be in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and headed for the entranceway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:06.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that Yutaka-san took the boat and left the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot be absolutely certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was the last time I saw Yutaka-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What time was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was around 1 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One slip and I'll be falling to the bottom of the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm with her when I fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'll probably have a higher chance of surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The cruiser's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:38.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really Yutaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gray sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It reminds me of being in closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I'm just not fond of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...such monochrome worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:48.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:51.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did somebody else come outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the real perpetrator!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Haruhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:03.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it went this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no other path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:09.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:25.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:27.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a fine mess now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't look like we can go back the way we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it was warm inside the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it heat from the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or maybe it was heat from an underground spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that shadow was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:55.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't just seeing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:07.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think Yutaka-san killed Keiichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing some thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on Mori-san's testimony...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yutaka-san left this island late last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I touched Keiichi-san earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...his body still felt warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Keiichi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...hadn't been dead long when we found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-san left the villa the night of the typhoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lurked around the island for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...before stabbing Keiichi-san and running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:43.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you assume that Keiichi-san was killed an hour before we found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we were all awake and moving around the house at that time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:51.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be unnatural for us not to hear a sound or scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that Keiichi-san was still alive for a few hours after being stabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and locked the door himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if Yutaka-san isn't even the perpetrator...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...what reason would he have to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:03.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth behind this murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You listening, Kyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that Yutaka-san stabbed Keiichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...he would have no reason to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know his reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Yutaka-san stabbed Keiichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it was a premeditated murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...they got into an argument, and he picked up a nearby fruit knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ended up using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the knife didn't reach his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife was obstructed by the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and didn't cause a fatal wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is when it got complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san fainted from the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon seeing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yutaka-san believed that he had killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is what happened next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san, who had merely fainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...remained unconscious until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Keiichi-san came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...he stood up in a dazed state...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and remembered that his brother had tried to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to think clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...he locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when tragedy struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:22.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san tripped over himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and fell on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the knife was driven into his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Keiichi-san met his demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How could everything happen so perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change what's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any other explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-san should have been able to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...if he had actually killed him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Keiichi-san's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...was lying face up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If your deduction were correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:53.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Keiichi-san would have been found lying face down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:55.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Haruhi's deduction ended up being a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then, what would be the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yutaka-san wasn't on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...at the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which would mean the real culprit was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:36.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:41.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinching food now, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:46.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring them to your room right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:50.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody already ate theirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This was Arakawa's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Arakawa hadn't eaten anything since morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I delivered his first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't embarrass your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told not to open the door for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would require me to violate the order not to open the door for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Asahina-san still unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:26.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I would assume so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I meant anyone who wasn't in the SOS Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fellow members of the SOS Brigade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not informed of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:40.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was merely instructed not to open the door for any person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:44.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan, you didn't say anything when I left the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:48.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not receive any instruction regarding opening the door from this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi's order has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:58.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or here, I'll override her order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's also here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:06.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be more flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...supposed to be Nagato's idea of a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give me a break, Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your face and expression never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I can only assume you're always serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we continue our investigation for the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not made out to be a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let the police handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:43.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:45.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You discussed such matters in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to play detective so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...what Suzumiya-san is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san's deduction was partially correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the last part was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san was stabbed by Yutaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-san made the wrong assumption and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That much is all correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san was awakened by our voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:19.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Keiichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and just as we were about to open the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Keiichi-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Respond if you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...he locked it in his dazed state...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:34.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when the knife was driven into Keiichi-san's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the perpetrator...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would be the ones who broke the door down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Arakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:52.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san probably realized this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:59.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding the truth within her own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:03.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your story makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's unfortunate that you learned the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I seal your lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...nobody will ever know of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the logical course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-kun is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a knife stuck in his chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be so evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as you keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:51.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi was killed by Yutaka-san who had secretly returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the killer knows the motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he was apparently an unusual character to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the police will buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:04.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as a precaution, we'll stab this body a few more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To make Yutaka-san's unusual character more pronounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:16.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The gig is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were soundly beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did what Kyon-kun told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:29.76,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fs34\bord0.2\be1\shad0\1c&H222222&\b1\frx0\fry-25\frz45\3c&H000013&\pos(153,186)}Ultra
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:29.76,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fs35\bord0.2\be1\shad0\1c&H222222&\b1\frx0\fry-10\frz39\3c&H000013&\pos(222,123)}Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:36.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the superhuman genius and ultra detective, Haruhi Suzumiya-sama's ultra deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:40.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's amazing how much you kiss your own ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As you're probably all aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Koizumi-kun, the Tamaru brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Arakawa-san, and Mori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...were putting on an act for us the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They even had a false "truth" prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite an elaborate performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was for a bit of entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A surprise party, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:01.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She probably knew everything from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fooled for a good part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The false "truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:11.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi-san's death was caused by the ones who broke down the door, Kyon and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's when I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:17.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was enough force to drive the knife into his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:20.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dent or scratch should have been left on the door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet there wasn't a scratch on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who actually noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it could have been a sturdy door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be insufficient evidence for you to suspect anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other discrepancies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When Koizumi-kun and Arakawa-san first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "It's been quite some time," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If Arakawa-san had been hired a week ago and this was their first meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...this greeting would be quite strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who noticed that one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when we were racing to Keiichi-san's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-kun went straight to Keiichi-san's room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he know which room it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:02.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that it was his first time in this villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not once, but twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wouldn't be that odd for him to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:11.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he found out which room was mine in his own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the final piece of the puzzle was the food Kyon saw in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon. You explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:24.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person here who ate using knife and fork was Keiichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:29.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there was a possibility that Arakawa-san ate using knife and fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the issue would be that the carrots were left untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:36.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I got the idea that it might have been eaten by Keiichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:41.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at all the evidence before us, there can be only one conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Keiichi-san is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a rehearsed performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure that in Haruhi's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she's hearing a standing ovation a hundred times larger than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:56.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we put on an act of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the fighting I saw on the balcony was just an act, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for the call in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning on coming clean eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't expect to be caught so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deduction got us on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary, my dear Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So your organization was pulling the strings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tamaru brothers, Arakawa-san, and Mori-san are all my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}How did you like my ultra deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:40.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent Suzumiya-san from getting any strange ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Wasn't I cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I concluded that preparing an incident beforehand would be the best idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The little sister's presence was unexpected though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,During the trip here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:53.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you said that the "Agency" wasn't involved this time, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly have told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:58.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth now, could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:03.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you realize the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:07.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An incident like this couldn't really happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:13.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:17.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Haruhi would never truly wish for a murder to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:19.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:23.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have faith in Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:30.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:32.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspicious shadow Haruhi saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was also your doing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:37.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:39.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for me to continue acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was that shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san wished...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:50.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a perpetrator that wasn't one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If that was created by Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:02.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...still has some unknown being lurking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Haruhi was just seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the Bermuda Triangle?
